---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;

const title = "MuleSoft API Program Starter Kit";
const description = "Standardized Mule 4 project foundation with embedded enterprise standards.";
const githubRepo = "https://github.com/shrimante/mulesoft-api-program-starter-kit";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title={`${title} | Engineering Accelerators`}
  description={description}
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <a href="/accelerators" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-accent transition-colors mb-12 group text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
        Back to Accelerators
      </a>

      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-8 -top-8 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-accent uppercase bg-accent/5 rounded-full border border-accent/10">
          Delivery Accelerator
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter mb-6 italic">
          {title}
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          A governed, production-ready foundation for Mule 4 API programs that embeds enterprise observability and error handling standards into every new project.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href={githubRepo} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-slate-900 text-white hover:bg-accent text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-widest rounded-xl transition-all shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path></svg>
            View Repository
          </a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl mb-12 border border-slate-200 bg-white/50">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight italic">1. Eliminating Bootstrap Chaos</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            New MuleSoft projects often suffer from inconsistent project structures, fragmented property loading strategies, and ad-hoc observability. This starter kit eliminates "bootstrap chaos" by providing an opinionated, governed foundation that embeds enterprise engineering standards from day one.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl mb-12 border border-slate-200 bg-white/50">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight italic">2. Mandatory Core Dependencies</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Unlike generic templates, this starter kit concretely integrates the previous accelerators as mandatory baseline dependencies:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              <span><strong>Observability Standard:</strong> All flows are pre-wired with the <code>mulesoft-logging-correlation-standard</code>, ensuring unbroken correlation traces and structured JSON logging out of the box.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              <span><strong>Canonical Error Framework:</strong> The <code>mulesoft-error-handling-standard</code> is imported as the default global strategy, ensuring every API response adheres to the enterprise canonical model.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              <span><strong>Environment Property Strategy:</strong> Standardized loading for local, dev, test, and prod, including secure property vaulting via AES-256 encryption.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              <span><strong>MUnit Baseline:</strong> A pre-configured testing suite that validates correlation propagation and error mapping, ensuring high-quality deployments.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl mb-12 border border-slate-200 bg-slate-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight italic relative z-10">Governance Checklist</h2>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6 text-slate-300">
            <p>Every API delivered via this starter kit must adhere to the <strong>Definition of Done (DoD)</strong>:</p>
            <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm font-mono mt-4">
              <li class="bg-white/5 p-3 rounded border border-white/10 text-slate-300 whitespace-nowrap">✓ Standard Logging Integrated</li>
              <li class="bg-white/5 p-3 rounded border border-white/10 text-slate-300 whitespace-nowrap">✓ Canonical Error Handling Wired</li>
              <li class="bg-white/5 p-3 rounded border border-white/10 text-slate-300 whitespace-nowrap">✓ Correlation ID Traceable</li>
              <li class="bg-white/5 p-3 rounded border border-white/10 text-slate-300 whitespace-nowrap">✓ Secure Property Vaulting</li>
              <li class="bg-white/5 p-3 rounded border border-white/10 text-slate-300 whitespace-nowrap">✓ 80%+ MUnit Code Coverage</li>
              <li class="bg-white/5 p-3 rounded border border-white/10 text-slate-300 whitespace-nowrap">✓ Layer-Aware Design (S/P/E)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl mb-12 border border-slate-200 bg-white/50">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight italic">Standardized POM Structure</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">The <code>pom.xml</code> enforces the consumption of shared engineering accelerators, ensuring that delivery teams spend time on business logic rather than framework wiring.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-6 overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="text-sm text-green-400 font-mono">{"<"}dependency{">"}
  {"<"}groupId{">"}com.enterprise.architecture{"</"}groupId{">"}
  {"<"}artifactId{">"}mulesoft-logging-correlation-standard{"</"}artifactId{">"}
  {"<"}version{">"}1.0.0{"</"}version{">"}
  {"<"}classifier{">"}mule-plugin{"</"}classifier{">"}
{"</"}dependency{">"}

{"<"}dependency{">"}
  {"<"}groupId{">"}com.enterprise.architecture{"</"}groupId{">"}
  {"<"}artifactId{">"}mulesoft-error-handling-standard{"</"}artifactId{">"}
  {"<"}version{">"}1.0.0{"</"}version{">"}
  {"<"}classifier{">"}mule-plugin{"</"}classifier{">"}
{"</"}dependency{">"}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Footer CTA -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a href={githubRepo} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-200 text-sm uppercase font-bold tracking-widest rounded-xl transition-all font-mono">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path></svg>
          Explore the Full Starter Kit on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
